imdb.title: Conception: Ore no Kodomo wo Undekure!
imdb.plot: A high school student is transported to a fantasy world under danger, where he must sire superhuman children with mystical females that will save the world.

episodes.title: My Child?!
episodes.plot: High school student Yuge Itsuki is sent off to the magical world of Granvania with his childhood friend Konatsuki Mahiru. Itsuki was summoned to save this world, but to accomplish this mission he must perform Love Rituals?!

episodes.title: I Want You to Have My Child
episodes.plot: Itsuki and Mahiru performed their first Love Ritual and a Star Child was born! Later, Itsuki starts to bond with one of the maidens, Ruka, at the cherry blossom viewing welcome party.

episodes.title: Secrets in the Early Afternoon
episodes.plot: Itsuki bonds with Yuzuha, Maiden of Pisces. She works as a painter, but uses a coffin as bed for some reason, and drew what she saw in dreams while sleeping inside it. She seems to be in a slump, so Itsuki asks her out on a date as a change of pace.

episodes.title: I've Got So Many Kids
episodes.plot: A beach tour was organized to deepen Itsuki's bond with the maidens. However, that information was leaked to the biggest playboy in the academy, Seiya, who followed them in an attempt to seduce the maidens.

episodes.title: Let's Try Giving Birth, Together
episodes.plot: Itsuki finds out about the Stardust Labyrinths where the Impurity Lords dwell, as well as the 13th labyrinth and the existence of the 13th maiden. He sets out to find the maiden, however the maiden might actually be a boy?!

episodes.title: My Children, Thirteen of Them!?
episodes.plot: A girl claiming to be the 13th maiden shows up before Itsuki. She sets out to confess her love while wearing an outlandish '80s outfit. However, Itsuki fails to notice, and continues his search.
